Note:
sys/os/core/permissions.runa
File Permissions and User/Group Management

This module provides file permission management and user/group operations
for cross-platform access control. Includes support for POSIX permissions,
Windows ACLs, and user identity management.
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

Note: =====================================================================
Note: FILE PERMISSION OPERATIONS
Note: =====================================================================

Process called "get_file_permissions" that takes path as String returns FilePermissions:
    Note: Get file permissions for specified path
    Note: TODO: Implement file permission retrieval
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "File permission retrieval not yet implemented"

Process called "set_file_permissions" that takes path as String, permissions as FilePermissions returns Nothing:
    Note: Set file permissions for specified path
    Note: TODO: Implement file permission setting
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "File permission setting not yet implemented"

Process called "chmod" that takes path as String, mode as Integer returns Nothing:
    Note: Change file mode (POSIX-style permissions)
    Note: TODO: Implement chmod operation
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "chmod operation not yet implemented"

Process called "can_read" that takes path as String returns Boolean:
    Note: Check if current user can read file
    Note: TODO: Implement read permission check
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Read permission check not yet implemented"

Process called "can_write" that takes path as String returns Boolean:
    Note: Check if current user can write to file
    Note: TODO: Implement write permission check
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Write permission check not yet implemented"

Process called "can_execute" that takes path as String returns Boolean:
    Note: Check if current user can execute file
    Note: TODO: Implement execute permission check
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Execute permission check not yet implemented"

Note: =====================================================================
Note: OWNERSHIP OPERATIONS
Note: =====================================================================

Process called "get_file_owner" that takes path as String returns UserInfo:
    Note: Get file owner information
    Note: TODO: Implement file owner retrieval
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "File owner retrieval not yet implemented"

Process called "set_file_owner" that takes path as String, user_id as Integer returns Nothing:
    Note: Set file owner by user ID
    Note: TODO: Implement file owner setting
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "File owner setting not yet implemented"

Process called "chown" that takes path as String, user_id as Integer, group_id as Integer returns Nothing:
    Note: Change file ownership (POSIX chown)
    Note: TODO: Implement chown operation
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "chown operation not yet implemented"

Process called "get_file_group" that takes path as String returns GroupInfo:
    Note: Get file group information
    Note: TODO: Implement file group retrieval
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "File group retrieval not yet implemented"

Note: =====================================================================
Note: USER MANAGEMENT OPERATIONS
Note: =====================================================================

Process called "get_current_user" returns UserInfo:
    Note: Get information about current user
    Note: TODO: Implement current user info retrieval
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Current user info retrieval not yet implemented"

Process called "get_user_by_id" that takes user_id as Integer returns UserInfo:
    Note: Get user information by user ID
    Note: TODO: Implement user lookup by ID
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "User lookup by ID not yet implemented"

Process called "get_user_by_name" that takes username as String returns UserInfo:
    Note: Get user information by username
    Note: TODO: Implement user lookup by name
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "User lookup by name not yet implemented"

Process called "list_users" returns List:
    Note: List all system users
    Note: TODO: Implement user listing
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "User listing not yet implemented"

Note: =====================================================================
Note: GROUP MANAGEMENT OPERATIONS
Note: =====================================================================

Process called "get_current_group" returns GroupInfo:
    Note: Get information about current user's primary group
    Note: TODO: Implement current group info retrieval
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Current group info retrieval not yet implemented"

Process called "get_group_by_id" that takes group_id as Integer returns GroupInfo:
    Note: Get group information by group ID
    Note: TODO: Implement group lookup by ID
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Group lookup by ID not yet implemented"

Process called "get_group_by_name" that takes groupname as String returns GroupInfo:
    Note: Get group information by group name
    Note: TODO: Implement group lookup by name
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Group lookup by name not yet implemented"

Process called "get_user_groups" that takes user_id as Integer returns List:
    Note: Get all groups that user belongs to
    Note: TODO: Implement user group membership query
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "User group membership query not yet implemented"

Process called "list_groups" returns List:
    Note: List all system groups
    Note: TODO: Implement group listing
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Group listing not yet implemented"

Note: =====================================================================
Note: ACCESS CONTROL OPERATIONS
Note: =====================================================================

Process called "check_access" that takes path as String, user_id as Integer, access_type as String returns Boolean:
    Note: Check if user has specific access to file
    Note: TODO: Implement access checking
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Access checking not yet implemented"

Process called "get_effective_permissions" that takes path as String, user_id as Integer returns EffectivePermissions:
    Note: Get effective permissions for user on file
    Note: TODO: Implement effective permission calculation
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Effective permission calculation not yet implemented"
